ariants, we\nalso demonstrate that $\\mathcal{N}=1$ localization is not possible for\nbackgrounds without R-symmetry.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 15 Dec 2014 21:15:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 16 Jan 2015 14:31:31 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 27 Feb 2015 16:11:18 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 7 May 2015 15:37:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-08"}
