er, using the same causality\narguments, one can constrain (or in some cases assist) the non-conventional\nscenarios of primordial magnetogenesis that amplify their fields during\ninflation. Finally, we show that our results extend naturally to the marginally\nopen and the marginally closed Friedmann universes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 15 Dec 2014 21:19:29 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 30 Dec 2015 18:37:18 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 21 Dec 2016 18:18:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-05-11"}
